机枪凯利在“尴尬”的巴西大奖赛采访后回应批评https://www.nme.com/news/music/machine-gun-kelly-responds-to-criticism-after-awkward-brazilian-grand-prix-interview-3531922?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=machine-gun-凯利在尴尬的巴西大奖赛采访后回应批评Liberty DunworthMon, 06 Nov 2023 12:36:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3531922 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="机枪凯利于 2023 年 8 月 13 日在 2023 年机枪凯利日期间登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这一刻的视频在网上疯传</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/machine-gun-kelly-responds-to-criticism-after-awkward-brazilian-grand-prix-interview-3531922">《机关枪》凯利在“尴尬”的巴西大奖赛采访后对批评做出了回应，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="机枪凯利于 2023 年 8 月 13 日在 2023 年机枪凯利日期间登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Machine-Gun-Kelly@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-